        performing in the live band - Lucky Stone.
        <br />
         Thank you, Bryan!
      </p>

      <b>Jessie</b>
      <p>
        Jessie is a member of the FOLP and is experience-focused - for both
        attendees and volunteers - and values community outreach. Jessie has the
