        cause. She is also performing in the live music band - Lucky Stone.
        <br />
         Thank you, Jessie!
      </p>

      <b>Jenny</b>
      <p>
        Jenny is a member of the FOLP and is the overseer of vendor land! She
        can problem-solve, assemble groups, and push an event to new heights -
        all with a baby strapped to her back. Her knowledge and experience are
        very much appreciated.
        <br />Thank you, Jenny!
      </p>

      <b>Patty</b>
      <p>
        Patty is the secretary of FOLP and queen of beverages and crafts. Patty
        has recruited some of our favorite breweries to the event, and is one of
        the live music acts - PJ’s Pub Tour! Her dedication to the event has
        helped make it possible.
        <br />Thank you, Patty!
      </p>

