        Thank you for your incredible dedication and hard work in making Pond
        Fest a reality! Your time, energy, and enthusiasm have brought this
        event to life, and we couldn’t have done it without you. Whether you
        were behind the scenes or front and center during the event, your
        contributions have created a positive impact on Lums Pond State Park and
        the community we serve. Your commitment not only helps raise essential
        funds for the park but also fosters the spirit of togetherness and
        volunteerism that makes our park and events so special.
      </p>

